// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0135 — Mass File Rename (maze)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 81069ad8-2950-54ab-b787-9bb04fe098dc

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
